------------------------------------------------------------------------

ConsoleRDP composes the following third-party software at runtime. They
are NOT redistributed inside this repository; they are pulled from the
host distribution at install time. Their respective licenses apply to
those binaries:

  - xrdp ............ Apache-2.0
  - xorgxrdp ........ X11/MIT
  - x11vnc .......... GPL-2.0-or-later
  - xinput .......... MIT
  - kbd (chvt) ...... GPL-2.0-or-later
  - systemd ......... LGPL-2.1-or-later
  - SDDM ............ GPL-2.0-or-later (host display manager)

If you redistribute a system image bundling these together with
ConsoleRDP, the strongest copyleft term among the included components
governs that combined distribution. ConsoleRDP itself, as authored in
this repository, is Apache-2.0.
